metadata.name: Inside
metadata.description: We may see people in life who look happy or fancy, or people who put on make-up, often as if for beauty, but some of them do it to hide a sadness, if the eyes never lie. If you look into their eyes, you can see the inner feeling of that person, we may see a person with a happy appearance, but inside she is full of sadness or a person with a happy appearance but an inner full of anger or ...
